#
# The store is a flat document keyspace (ADR-0017 d1/d15). Markdown documents that
# live here (e.g. the M Manual SP0004-M-gateway-bringup.md) keep CRLF per the repo
# doc convention. Scoped to *.md so CRLF never touches the binary / generated
# hardware design files (gerbers, KiCad, drill, PNG), which git treats as binary.
*.md text eol=crlf
